data.description: Welcome Home!! This Beautiful  home features, 3 Bedroom with a bonus room/office, 5 bathrooms (3 full baths 2 half bath), a 2 car garage, double sided fireplace, large kitchen perfect for family gatherings. The master suite is located on the main floor, but there is two additional suits on the 2nd level. This home also included a balcony that over looks the first floor and the beautiful view of the back yard, swimming pool and the gazebo! In addition, this home also includes two over size decks perfect for entertainment and creating family memories,  over 7 acres of land, outside storage buildings, swimming pool, large gazebo and more! SOLD AS IS!!! A MUST SEE!!!
